Class FormatWriterText

java.lang.Object
us.irdev.bedrock.bag.formats.FormatWriter
us.irdev.bedrock.bag.formats.FormatWriterText
public class FormatWriterText extends FormatWriter
The FormatWriterText is a configurable text format writer for any format that uses a divider between entries, and a divider between pairs.
